Functions:

mean.sd<-function(y){
  tabla<-as.matrix(c(mean(y),sd(y)))
  rownames(tabla)<-c("mean","sd")
  return(tabla)
}
kurtosis.skewness<-function(y){
  tabla<-as.matrix(c(kurtosis(y),skewness(y)))
  return(tabla)
}
